#### **âœ… CORRECT: Telegram Topics Configuration**
```yaml
# âœ… CORRECT: User provided topic secret keys
name: ğŸ”¨ Build Notification
jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
    - name: ğŸ”¨ Build Complete
      uses: asychin/telegram-notify-action@v3.1.0
